Package: mapreliability
Title: Map Reliability Calculator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Maxwell", "Austensen", email = "m.austensen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tool for assessing the statistical reliability of classifications used in mapping, 
  adapted from NYC Department of City Planning's Excel-based Map Reliability Calculator.
